5	## St Andrews on a Shoestring\r\n\r\nOur Select Itineraries for golf in Scotland feature some of our most popular destinations, however if you wish to create a bespoke package please call our specialists or create your own.\r\n\r\n* Day 1 - Depart USA\r\n* Day 2 - Arrive Edinburgh / Glasgow, Travel to Fairmont St Andrews, Play Torrance Course, Fairmont (Includes lunch)\r\n* Day 3 - Play Old Course (Enter ballot, green fee payable locally)\r\n* Day 4 - Play New Course\r\n* Day 5 - Play Kingsbarns (Includes caddy and lunch)\r\n* Day 6 - Play Kittocks Course, Fairmont (Includes shared cart and lunch)\r\n* Day 7 - Play Carnoustie Championship\r\n* Day 8 - Depart Edinburgh / Glasgow, Arrive USA\r\n\r\n### What's included\r\n\r\n* 6 nights at Fairmont St Andrews - based on 2 sharing a twin room\r\n\r\n* Full Scottish breakfast each morning\r\n\r\n* 5 Green Fees for rounds of golf as above, excluding Old Course\r\n\r\n* Opel Zafira 7-seat vehicle or similar (incl Crash Damage Waiver, Unlimited mileage, Insurance and VAT)\r\n\r\n* All local taxes\r\n\r\n### Supplements\r\n\r\nChauffeur driven luxury coach with guide\r\n$ on request\r\n\r\n### Upgrade Options (per person)\r\n\r\nAvailable on request\r\n\r\nAll invoices will be in £'s sterling\r\nDollar prices are as a guide due to fluctuating exchange rates. Invoices will be in £'s Sterling as stated. 	## St Andrews on a Shoestring\r\n\r\nYour time on this tour will be spent in the luxurious surroundings of the five star Fairmont St Andrews. As well as enjoying the supreme restaurants and outstanding facilities this stunning resort hotel has to offer you will also head off to a new Scottish golfing gem each day including the St Andrews New and Old Courses, Kingsbarns and the devilishly difficult Carnoustie. Rounds on these courses will be supplemented by rounds on the Fairmont’s two home courses, the Kittocks and the Torrance which will complete your Scottish golf experience.		2079	1389	2011-08-30 15:29:32.478423	2011-09-1