12	Southport & British Open 	southport-british-open	# Southport & British Open \r\n\r\nNorth West England not only boasts great cities like Manchester, Leeds and Liverpool, it is also home to an outstanding collection of world class golf courses. The coast of West Lancashire is a golfer’s paradise thanks to countless Open Championship venues and a vast number of lesser known but equally impressive golfing gems. \r\n\r\nSouthport is surrounded by classic links courses including Royal Liverpool, Royal Lytham & St Anne’s and Royal Birkdale which is widely considered to be one of the finest golf courses anywhere in the world. All of these famous Open Championship venues are on the menu and the quality of these courses will be matched by the unsung heroes on the itinerary.\r\n\r\nHillside and Southport & Ainsdale are both breathtaking links layouts that share the same sandy turf and towering dunes as their more illustrious neighbours while Formby is one of the most interesting golf courses in the country. A links course by design, Formby is not situated directly adjacent to the coast and unlike other links courses it features towering pines that simply add to its mystique. \r\n\r\nThe golfing delights dotted around Southport can all be easily accessed from the stylish and sleek Vincent Hotel which is one of the finest and most sought after in the area. Perfect for the travelling golfer, The Vincent Hotel offers comfortable accommodation and a highly regarded bistro and bar that is the perfect place to discuss the day’s events from the one of the stunning surrounding golf courses.	2011-08-30 16:20:14.47227	2011-09-13 09:49:23.984674	tours	53.571307,-1.972046	9	England	British Open Golf Tours - Birkdale, Royal Liverpool | Your Golf Tours	\N
